race.comment: WOLF THUNDER (8) was a last start winner (18.87) at this track who is building a strong winning record. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Sure to prove hard to beat. SWING BY (1) has a strong record this trip with two wins and three placings from six starts. Missed the frame latest (18.89) when fourth over 350m at this track in a Grade 5. Looks one of the chances. IT'S TIME RED (2) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fourth (16.73) from Box 3 at this track over 300m. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from four starts. Cannot be taken lightly. BLUE LAKODA (7) showed plenty of dash to record a last start win. Hard to beat again.
